  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 350°F.",
    "In a large bowl, mix the flour with salt and pepper.",
    "Add heavy cream and butter to the bowl. Stir until it becomes a crumbly dough.",
    "If using Cream of Mushroom Soup Mix, combine it into the mixture before adding the soup base instructions.",
    "Transfer the mixture onto an ungreased baking sheet. Press down evenly.",
    "Bake in preheated oven for 15-20 minutes or until golden brown and crispy on top.",
    "Allow to cool slightly before serving."
